<h2 style=3D"text-align: left;" id=3D"HandoverfromDesignertoDeveloper-Desig=
nertoDeveloper">Designer to Developer</h2>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><strong=
>If you are not the developer of this API you must schedule a meeting with =
the developer who will be&nbsp;coding the API<br></strong></span></p>
