,0);">Deliverables </span></span></h2>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">The following will be required by the=
 Developer<br></span></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id=3D"HandoverfromDesignertoDeveloper-Swaggerspec"><span style=3D"c=
olor: rgb(102,102,153);">Swagger spec</span></h5></li>
